\cos x = 1  - \frac{x^2}{2} + \frac{x^4}{24} - \frac{x^6}{720}+ \frac{x^8}{40320}-\cdots
\sin x = x - \frac{x^3}{3!} + \frac{x^5}{5!} = \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^n}{(2n+1)!} x^{2n+1}
\cos x = 1  - \frac{x^2}{2!} + \frac{x^4}{4!} = \sum_{n=0}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^n}{(2n)!} x^{2n}
